<p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/IT_lesliewu/article/details/124893143?utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2~default~baidujs_baidulandingword~default-0-124893143-blog-128620393.pc_relevant_3mothn_strategy_and_data_recovery&amp;spm=1001.2101.3001.4242.1&amp;utm_relevant_index=3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">树莓派4B64位系统安装miniconda（折腾了几天终于解决）</a></p>
</li>
